        <p class="lead pb-2">
          üíù Donations are always appreciated!
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://donate.alexkaul.com/debitpay-directory" class="btn btn-secondary" target="_blank">Donate Bitcoin</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-5 text-center text-md-right pb-5">
